Name: LibClang
Cabal-version: >= 1.2
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Chetan Taralekar <chetant@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Chetan Taralekar <chetant@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/chetant/LibClang/issues
License: BSD3
License-file: LICENSE
Synopsis: Clang provides haskell bindings for libclang (a C++ parsing library)
Description:
  Clang package provides direct bindings to libclang.
  This should be enough for parsing C/C++ code, walking the AST and querying nodes.

  NOTE .. When configuring, please provide the location of libclang includes
       .. if not in the default locations using --extra-include-dirs=<LOCATION>
Category: Language
build-type: Configure

Library
  hs-source-dirs: src
  build-depends: base, ffi, greencard
  build-tools: greencard
  c-sources: src/Clang/FFI_stub_ffi.c
